<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Alerte plantation</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#f2f6f3; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#153b27;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#f2f6f3; padding:20px 0;">
    <tr>
        <td align="center">
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width:620px; background:#ffffff; border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid #dce9e1;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e6b4a,#2f8f62); padding:22px 24px;">
                        <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:22px; line-height:1.2; color:#ffffff; font-weight:700;">
                            FarmTech - Alerte jeu plantation
                        </h1>
                        <p style="margin:8px 0 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.4; color:#dff4e9;">
                            Une plante est morte naturellement dans le mini-jeu (et non via suppression manuelle).
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:22px 24px 8px;">
                        <p style="margin:0 0 14px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.55; color:#294434;">
                            Bonjour,<br>
                            une alerte a ete declenchee car une plante n'a pas ete traitee a temps.
                            Voici le detail de l'evenement:
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:0 24px 24px;">
                        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:separate; border-spacing:0; border:1px solid #e2eee7; border-radius:10px; overflow:hidden;">
                            <tr>
                                <td style="width:44%; background:#f7fbf8; padding:12px 14px; border-bottom:1px solid #e2eee7; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#325741;">
                                    Plante
                                </td>
                                <td style="padding:12px 14px; border-bottom:1px solid #e2eee7; font-size:14px; color:#153b27;">
                                    {{ plantName }}
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="width:44%; background:#f7fbf8; padding:12px 14px; border-bottom:1px solid #e2eee7; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#325741;">
                                    Cause
                                </td>
                                <td style="padding:12px 14px; border-bottom:1px solid #e2eee7; font-size:14px; color:#153b27;">
                                    {{ reasonLabel|default('Timer epuise') }}
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="width:44%; background:#f7fbf8; padding:12px 14px; {% if temp is not null %}border-bottom:1px solid #e2eee7;{% endif %} font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#325741;">
                                    Date / heure
                                </td>
                                <td style="padding:12px 14px; {% if temp is not null %}border-bottom:1px solid #e2eee7;{% endif %} font-size:14px; color:#153b27;">
                                    {{ occurredAt|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            {% if temp is not null %}
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="background:#f7fbf8; padding:12px 14px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#325741;">
                                        Temperature
                                    </td>
                                    <td style="padding:12px 14px; font-size:14px; color:#153b27;">
                                        {{ temp }} degC
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            {% endif %}
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:0 24px 24px;">
                        <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; color:#5f7c6a;">
                            Action recommandee: utilisez Engrais pour replanter la parcelle puis Eau regulierement pour eviter une nouvelle perte.
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:16px 24px; background:#f7fbf8; border-top:1px solid #e2eee7;">
                        <p style="margin:0; font-size:12px; line-height:1.5; color:#7a9586;">
                            Message automatique FarmTech.
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
